LUKE 19.45 jah galeiþands in alh dugann uswairpan þans frabugjandans in izai jah bugjandans, LUKE 19.46 qiþands du im:
gameliþ ist þatei
gards meins gards bido ist;
iþ jus ina gatawideduþ du filegrja þiube.
LUKE 19.47 jah was laisjands daga ƕammeh in þizai alh:
iþ þai auhmistans gudjans jah bokarjos sokidedun ina usqistjan jah þai frumistans manageins.
LUKE 19.48 jah ni bigetun ƕa gatawidedeina;
managei auk alakjo hahaida du hausjan imma.
LUKE 20.1 Jah warþ in sumamma dage jainaize at laisjandin imma þo managein in alh jah wailamerjandin, atstoþun þai gudjans jah bokarjos miþ þaim sinistam LUKE 20.2 jah qeþun du imma qiþandans:
qiþ unsis, in ƕamma waldufnje þata taujis, aiþþau ƕas ist saei gaf þus þata waldufni?
LUKE 20.3 andhafjands þan qaþ du im:
fraihna izwis jah ik ainis waurdis jah qiþiþ mis:
LUKE 20.4 daupeins Iohannis uzuh himina was þau uzuh mannam?
LUKE 20.5 iþ eis þahtedun miþ sis misso qiþandans þatei
jabai qiþam: us himina, qiþiþ:
aþþan duƕe ni galaubideduþ imma?
LUKE 20.6 iþ jabai qiþam: us mannam, alla so managei stainam afwairpiþ unsis;
triggwaba galaubjand auk allai Iohannen praufetu wisan.
LUKE 20.7 jah andhofun ei ni wissedeina ƕaþro.
LUKE 20.8 jah Iesus qaþ im:
ni ik izwis qiþa, in ƕamma waldufnje þata tauja.
LUKE 20.9 dugann þan du managein qiþan þo gajukon:
manna ussatida weinagard, jah anafalh ina waurstwjam jah aflaiþ jera ganoha.
LUKE 20.10 jah in mela insandida du þaim aurtjam skalk, ei akranis þis weinagardis gebeina imma.
iþ þai aurtjans usbliggwandans ina insandidedun lausana.
LUKE 20.11 jah anaaiauk sandjan anþarana skalk;
iþ eis jah jainana bliggwandans jah unswerandans insandidedun lausana.
LUKE 20.12 jah anaaiauk sandjan þridjan;
iþ eis jah þana gawondondans uswaurpun.
LUKE 20.13 qaþ þan sa frauja þis weinagardis:
ƕa taujau?
sandja sunu meinana þana liuban;
aufto þana gasaiƕandans aistand.
LUKE 20.14 gasaiƕandans þan ina þai aurtjans þahtedun miþ sis misso qiþandans,
sa ist sa arbinumja;
afslaham ina, ei uns wairþai þata arbi.
LUKE 20.15 jah uswairpandans ina ut us þamma weinagarda usqemun.
ƕa nu taujai im frauja þis weinagardis?
LUKE 20.16 qimiþ jah usqisteiþ aurtjam þaim jah gibiþ þana weinagard anþaraim.
gahausjandans qeþun þan:
nissijai.
LUKE 20.17 iþ is insaiƕands du im qaþ:
aþþan ƕa ist þata gamelido:
stains þammei uskusun timrjans, sah warþ du haubida waihstins?
LUKE 20.18 ƕazuh saei driusiþ ana þana stain, gakrotuda;
iþ ana þanei driusiþ, diswinþeiþ ina.
LUKE 20.19 jah sokidedun þai bokarjos jah auhumistans gudjans uslagjan ana ina handuns in þizai ƕeilai jah ohtedun þo managein;
froþun auk þatei du im þo gajukon qaþ.
LUKE 20.20 jah afleiþandans insandidedun ferjans, þans us liutein taiknjandans sik garaihtans wisan, ei gafaifaheina is waurdei jah atgebeina ina reikja jah waldufnja kindinis.
LUKE 20.21 jah frehun ina qiþandans:
laisari, witum þatei raihtaba rodeis jah laiseis jah ni andsaiƕis andwairþi, ak bi sunjai wig gudis laiseis:
LUKE 20.22 skuldu ist unsis kaisara gild giban þau niu?
LUKE 20.23 bisaiƕands þan ize unselein Iesus qaþ du im:
ƕa mik fraisiþ?
LUKE 20.24 ataugeiþ mis skatt:
ƕis habaiþ manleikan jah ufarmeli?

kaisaris.
LUKE 20.25 iþ is qaþuh du im:
us-gibiþ-nu þo kaisaris kaisara jah þo gudis guda.
LUKE 20.26 jah ni mahtedun gafahan is waurde in andwairþja manageins jah sildaleikjandans andawaurde is gaþahaidedun.
LUKE 20.27 du atgaggandans þan sumai Saddukaie, þaiei qiþand usstass ni wisan, frehun ina LUKE 20.28 qiþandans:
